<section id="rotation">
	<h2>Rotation</h2>

	<h3>Single Target Rotation</h3>
	<ol>
		<li>Keep Consecration active.</li>
		<li>Use Shield of the Righteous for uptime and armor.</li>
		<li>Use Avenger's Shield on cooldown.</li>
		<li>Use Judgment for Holy Power and debuff.</li>
		<li>Use Hammer of the Righteous or Blessed Hammer as filler.</li>
		<li>Use Word of Glory with Shining Light procs when needed.</li>
	</ol>

	<h3>AoE Rotation</h3>
	<ol>
		<li>Maintain Consecration in AoE packs.</li>
		<li>Use Avenger's Shield — it bounces and silences.</li>
		<li>Hammer of the Righteous hits multiple targets in Consecration.</li>
		<li>Use Divine Toll to open pulls and generate threat.</li>
		<li>Prioritize Shield of the Righteous uptime.</li>
	</ol>

	<h3>Cooldown Usage</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Ardent Defender — for cheat death or big hits.</li>
		<li>Guardian of Ancient Kings — reduce massive damage.</li>
		<li>Divine Shield — last resort immunity.</li>
		<li>Eye of Tyr — use on cooldown for AoE mitigation.</li>
		<li>Avenging Wrath — burst phases or big pulls.</li>
		<li>Moment of Glory — big pulls with Avenger’s Shield.</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Defensive Priority</h3>
	<ol>
		<li>Always maintain Consecration uptime.</li>
		<li>Keep Shield of the Righteous active.</li>
		<li>Use Word of Glory when needed.</li>
		<li>Use cooldowns preemptively.</li>
		<li>Position mobs in Consecration and kite when needed.</li>
	</ol>
</section>

